---
title: Charred Avocado Cavatappi with Green Onions, Heirloom Tomatoes, and Feta
description: If you thought avocado couldn’t get any creamier, you were wrong. A quick char in the pan (or flash on the grill!) makes luscious avocado that much better. Tossed with juicy heirloom tomatoes and lightly charred green onions, this might be your new go-to easy pasta supper!
